{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, the word Anamnese is not part of the gbert vocabulary.",
    "This makes a verbalizer search for clinicians quite challenging.",
    "Therefore, we use PET with automatic labels (PETAL) for all our experiments, except for the zero-shot baselines (Schick et al. 2020).",
    "This can reduce engineering costs and makes our experimental setup more comparable and reproducible.",
    "As visualized in Suppl."
  ]
}